#. Tag: title
#: thumbnail-view.docbook:9
#, no-c-format
msgid "Thumbnail viewer"
msgstr "Umanjeni preglednik"

#. Tag: para
#: thumbnail-view.docbook:10
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Selecting <guilabel>View Thumbnails</guilabel> in the browser, you get to a "
"thumbnail overview of the images currently in scope (or all images if no "
"scope have been selected). An example of this can be seen in <xref linkend="
"\"fig-thumbnailview\"/> below. The size of the thumbnails can be configure "
"simply by dragging the mouse with the middle mouse button down (try it is "
"really cool)."
msgstr ""
"Izbor <guilabel>Preglednik Sličica</guilabel> u pretraživaču, dobijate na "
"umanjenom pregledniku  slike u trenutnom obimu (ili sve slike ako nije "
"izabran nijedan opseg). Primjer za to se može vidjeti u <xref linkend=\"fig-"
"thumbnailview\"/> u nastavku. Veličina sličice se može konfigurirati "
"jednostavno povlačenjem miša uz pritisnutu srednju tipku miša (pokušajte "
"stvarno je super)."

#. Tag: title
#: thumbnail-view.docbook:18
#, no-c-format
msgid "Thumbnail View"
msgstr "Umanjeni pregled"

#. Tag: para
#: thumbnail-view.docbook:26
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"In the thumbnail overview you can reorder your pictures by dragging them "
"around with the mouse. For the date bar to work properly you should, "
"however, aim at keeping your images sorted at all time. Sorting you images "
"can be done by selecting all images, and choosing "
"<menuchoice><guimenu>Images</guimenu><guimenuitem>Sort Selected by Date "
"&amp; Time</guimenuitem></menuchoice>. The sorting will not reorder images "
"which has the same date and time, so if you have say 100 images with the "
"date 1992 (i.e. no month, no day, only year), then you may move them around, "
"and their individual order will stay unchanged after a sort."
msgstr ""
"U umanjenom pregledniku možete preurediti svoje slike povlačenjem  s mišem. "
"Za datum traku koja radi ispravno, međutim, cilj je u čuvanju svojih slika "
"sortiranih u svakom trenutku. Sortiranje vaših slika se može učiniti izborom "
"svih slika, i odabirom <menuchoice><guimenu>Slike</guimenu><guimenuitem> "
"Sortiranje odabrano po datumu &amp;Vrijeme</guimenuitem></menuchoice>. "
"Sortiranje neće preurediti slike koje imaju isti datum i vrijeme, tako da "
"ako imate recimo 100 slika s datumom 1992. godine (tj nema mjeseca, nema "
"dana, samo godinu), a zatim ih možete pomjerati, a  njihov pojedinačni oblik "
"će tako ostati nepromijenjen nakon sortiranja."

#. Tag: para
#: thumbnail-view.docbook:35
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Dragging an image from the viewer to the background will set the image as "
"the background image of your desktop."
msgstr ""
"Povlačenje slike iz prikaznika u pozadinu će postaviti sliku kao sliku "
"pozadine na vašem desktopu."

#. Tag: para
#: thumbnail-view.docbook:38
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"By clicking on an image you load it into the viewer, if no viewer window is "
"present, a viewer window will be created."
msgstr ""
"Klikom na sliku koju učitavate u prikaznik, ako nije prisutan prikazni "
"prozor , onda će biti kreiran prikazni prozor."

#. Tag: para
#: thumbnail-view.docbook:41
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"If you select a number of images, and presses <keycombo>&Ctrl;<keycap>I</"
"keycap></keycombo> or chooses <menuchoice><guimenu>Images</"
"guimenu><guimenuitem>View Selected</guimenuitem></menuchoice>, the images "
"will be loaded into the existing viewer (if no viewer exists, one will be "
"created). Alternatively you may choose <menuchoice><guimenu>Images</"
"guimenu><guimenuitem>View (in new window)</guimenuitem></menuchoice> to get "
"the images loaded into a new viewer. If you press <keycombo>&Ctrl;<keycap>R</"
"keycap></keycombo> or choose <menuchoice><guimenu>Images</"
"guimenu><guimenuitem>Run Slide Show</guimenuitem></menuchoice> the selected "
"images will be loaded into the viewer and a slide show will start. Finally "
"choosing <menuchoice><guimenu>Images</guimenu><guimenuitem>Run Randomized "
"Slide Show</guimenuitem></menuchoice> will show a slide show of the images "
"selected in random order."
msgstr ""
"Ako odaberete broj slika, i pretisnete <keycombo>&Ctrl;<keycap>I</keycap></"
"keycombo> ili birte<menuchoice><guimenu>Slike</guimenu><guimenuitem>Prikaz "
"Odabranih</guimenuitem></menuchoice>, slike će se učitati u postojeći "
"Prikaznik (ako ne postoji Prikaznik, jedan će biti kreiran). Alternativno "
"možete odabrati <menuchoice><guimenu>Slike</guimenu> <guimenuitem>Prikaznik "
"(u novom prozoru)</guimenuitem></menuchoice> da biste dobili slike učitane u "
"novom prikazniku. Ako pritisnete <keycombo>&Ctrl;<keycap>R</keycap></"
"keycombo> ili odaberite<menuchoice><guimenu>Slike</"
"guimenu><guimenuitem>Pokreni prezentaciju</guimenuitem></menuchoice> "
"izabrane slike će se učitati u Prikaznik i prezentacija će početi. Konačno "
"odabirom <menuchoice><guimenu>Slike</guimenu><guimenuitem>Pokreni nasumice "
"prezentaciju</guimenuitem></menuchoice> će pokazati slajdove slika izabranih "
"u slučajnom redoslijedu."

#. Tag: title
#: thumbnail-view.docbook:56 thumbnail-view.docbook:64
#, no-c-format
msgid "Deleting Images"
msgstr "Brisanje slika"

#. Tag: para
#: thumbnail-view.docbook:57
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"From the thumbnail view it is also possible to delete images. To do so "
"select the images you want to delete and press the delete key or select "
"<menuchoice><guimenu>Edit</guimenu><guimenuitem>Delete Selected</"
"guimenuitem></menuchoice> from the menu bar. Doing so &kphotoalbum; will "
"show you the dialog in <xref linkend=\"fig-delete-images\"/>"
msgstr ""
"Sa umanjenog pregleda  također je moguće izbrisati slike. Da biste to "
"učinili, odaberite slike koje želite izbrisati i pritisnite delete ili "
"odaberite<menuchoice><guimenu>Uredi</guimenu><guimenuitem>Izbriši odabrano</"
"guimenuitem></menuchoice> na traci menija.Radeći to &kphotoalbum; će vam "
"pokazati dijalog u <xref linkend=\"fig-delete-images\"/>"

#. Tag: para
#: thumbnail-view.docbook:72
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"There are three ways of deleting an image in &kphotoalbum;, namely move to "
"thrash, delete it from the disk - which means that it will be permanently "
"gone - or tell &kphotoalbum; not to include it. In the latter case, "
"&kphotoalbum; will never show the image again, but it will keep it on disk. "
"This is useful if there for example is <emphasis>thumbnail images</emphasis> "
"stored among your images. This thumbnail image would contain an overview of "
"all the other images, and would thus be useless in &kphotoalbum;, but for "
"other application, say a web browser, it might be needed."
msgstr ""
"Postoje tri načina za brisanje slike u &kphotoalbum;, naime preći na kantu, "
"izbrisati ga sa diska - što znači da će  trajno nestati - ili recimo "
"&kphotoalbum; da ga ne uključuje. U prethodnom slučaju,  &kphotoalbum; "
"nikada neće pokazati sliku ponovo, ali će je zadržati na disku. Ovo je "
"korisno ako postoji, na primer, <emphasis>umanjene slike</emphasis> "
"pohranjene među vašim slikama. Ova sličica će sadržavati pregled svih "
"ostalih slika, a to bi bilo beskorisno u &kphotoalbum;, već i u drugim "
"aplikacijama, ali recimo za web preglednik, to bi moglo biti uistinu "
"potrebno."

#. Tag: title
#: thumbnail-view.docbook:84
#, no-c-format
msgid "Offline Mode"
msgstr "Offline režim"

#. Tag: para
#: thumbnail-view.docbook:85
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"There is a constant battle going on between data growing, and hard disks "
"getting bigger. If you have a large number of images, you might find "
"yourself in the middle of that battle, not having enough hard disk space to "
"store all your images. In that situation you might choose to put some of the "
"images on CD's. An alternative scenario might be that you are going on a "
"business trip, and want to bring your images with you, but do not have the "
"20GB disk space requires for that purpose."
msgstr ""
"Tu je stalna borba kako podaci rastu, i hard diskovi postaju sve veći. Ako "
"imate veliki broj slika, možda se nađete usred te borbe, nemajući dovoljno "
"prostora na hard disku za pohranu svih vaših slika. U toj situaciji možda "
"želite da stavite neke slike na CD-e. Alternativni scenario može biti da "
"idete na poslovni put, a želite ponijeti svoje slike sa sobom, ali nemate "
"dovoljno prostora na disku od 20GB koji sa zahtijeva za tu svrhu."

#. Tag: para
#: thumbnail-view.docbook:93
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"&kphotoalbum; offers a solution to that problem, namely that it allows you "
"to use it, without having the images available on disk. You do of course "
"need to have them available at some point in time for &kphotoalbum; to "
"realize that there are new images for it to index. <xref linkend=\"fig-"
"offline-mode\"/> shows &kphotoalbum; when it is not capable of finding all "
"needed images on the disk."
msgstr ""
"&kphotoalbum; nudi rješenje za taj problem, a to je da vam omogućava  da ga "
"koristite, bez dostupnih slika na disku. Naravno vi trebate da ih u nekom "
"trenutku imate dostupne za &kphotoalbum; da shvatite da postoje nove slike "
"za to u indeksu. <xref linkend=\"fig-offline-mode\"/>pokazuje &kphotoalbum; "
"kada nije u stanju pronaći sve potrebne slike na disku."

#. Tag: title
#: thumbnail-view.docbook:101
#, no-c-format
msgid "&kphotoalbum; in Offline Mode"
msgstr "&kphotoalbum; u Offline režimu"

#. Tag: para
#: thumbnail-view.docbook:109
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Images which have the corner cut of (that is images 1-4) are not available "
"on disk. Thumbnails are, available for images 5-9, even though the images "
"are missing from disk. Therefore &kphotoalbum; can show you the thumbnails "
"for these images but you cannot view them in the viewer. (We used to cut of "
"the corner of thumbnails to indicate the image is missing from disk but that "
"feature seems to be currently broken.)"
msgstr ""
"Slike koje imaju izrezani ugao (to su slike 1-4) nisu dostupne na disku. "
"Sličice su, na raspolaganju za slike 5-9, iako  slike nedostaju s diska. "
"Stoga &kphotoalbum; može prikazati sličice za ove slike, ali ne možete ih "
"videti u prikazniku. (Mi smo isjekli na uglu sličice da bi ukazali da slika "
"nedostaje iz diska, ali čini se da ovo svojstvo  trenutno ne radi.)"

#. Tag: para
#: thumbnail-view.docbook:117
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"As you can see, this feature requires you to copy files in and out of your "
"directories, &kphotoalbum; does not have any support for asking you to "
"insert the CD you labeled blah blah. Thus please forget about this feature "
"if you are the kind of person who do not like messing with files etc, and "
"instead simply ensure to buy hard disks that is large enough to always store "
"all your images."
msgstr ""
"Kao što vidite, ova opcija zahtijeva da kopirate datoteke  iz vaših "
"direktorija,  &kphotoalbum; nema podršku da zatraži  da ubacite CD  označen "
"sa bla bla. Stoga molimo zaboravite ovu opciju ako ste tip osobe koji ne "
"voli petljati s datotekama, itd, i umjesto toga jednostavno osigurajte sebe "
"sa hard diskovima koji su dovoljno veliki da uvijek čuvaju sve vaše slike."

#. Tag: title
#: thumbnail-view.docbook:129
#, no-c-format
msgid "Privacy"
msgstr "Privatnost"

#. Tag: para
#: thumbnail-view.docbook:130
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Some time ago my girlfriend and I brought my laptop with us on a visit to my "
"parents in law, to show them the images from our most recent holiday. "
"&kphotoalbum; turned out to be a great success, and it didn't last long "
"before my girlfriends little sister seized the laptop and started browsing "
"around on her own. Unfortunately it didn't take her long either to get to "
"some, let say unfortunate, images of me from my youth, and they all had "
"quite a bit of laugh on me. That episode inspired me to add a new feature to "
"&kphotoalbum;, namely privacy locking."
msgstr ""
"Prije nekog vremena moja djevojka i ja smo ponijeli moj laptop u posjetu "
"njenim roditeljima, da im pokažemo slike sa našeg najnovijeg odmora. "
"&kphotoalbum; ispostavilo se velikim uspjehom, ali to nije dugo potrajalo  "
"jer je od moje djevojke  mlađa sestra oduzela laptop i počela da pregleda  "
"sama. Nažalost, nije joj trebalo  dugo da pronađe recimo  neke, nesretne "
"slike iz moje mladosti, i svi su se dosta smijali na moj račun. Ta epizoda "
"me je inspirisala da dodam novu mogućnost da &kphotoalbum;, zaključavanjem "
"privatnosti."

#. Tag: para
#: thumbnail-view.docbook:139
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"In the <guimenu>Images</guimenu> menu you will find a sub menu called "
"<guimenuitem>privacy</guimenuitem>. To get some privacy, browse - while you "
"are on your own - to the images that you want to keep private, and select "
"<guimenuitem>Lock Away Current Set of Images</guimenuitem> from the privacy "
"sub menu. Alternatively you may browse to the images you want to limit your "
"little sister to see, and select <guimenuitem>Lock Away All Other Images</"
"guimenuitem>."
msgstr ""
"U <guimenu>Slike</guimenu> naći ćete podmeni imena <guimenuitem>privatnost</"
"guimenuitem>. Da bi dobili malo privatnosti, kada pregledavate - dok ste "
"sami - na slikama koje želite zadržati privatnim, i odaberite "
"<guimenuitem>Zaključaj trenutni niz slika</guimenuitem> iz privatnog "
"podmenija. Alternativno možete pregledati  slike koje želite ograničiti "
"svojoj mlađoj sestri da vidi, i odaberite<guimenuitem>Zaključaj sve sve "
"ostale slike</guimenuitem>."

#. Tag: para
#: thumbnail-view.docbook:147
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Now you have specified what to hide away, and once you hand over your laptop "
"to your little sister, simply choose <guimenuitem>Lock Images</guimenuitem>, "
"and your sister will not be able to see the locked images. When done you may "
"unlock them again using <guimenuitem>Unlock</guimenuitem>."
msgstr ""
"Sada ste odredili šta treba sakriti, a jednom kada predate laptop u ruke "
"vađe mlađe sestre, jednostavno odaberite <guimenuitem>Zaključaj slike</"
"guimenuitem>, i vaša sestra neće moći vidjeti zaključane slike. Kada "
"završite možete ih otključati ponovno koristeći <guimenuitem>Otključaj</"
"guimenuitem>."

#. Tag: para
#: thumbnail-view.docbook:153
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"It is possible to specify a password that must be entered to unlock the "
"database. In the <guimenuitem>privacy</guimenuitem> menu, simply select "
"<guimenuitem>Change Password</guimenuitem> to set a password."
msgstr ""
"Moguće je odrediti lozinku koja se mora unijeti za otključavanje baze "
"podataka. U <guimenuitem>privatnost</guimenuitem> meni, jednostavno  "
"odaberite <guimenuitem>Promijeni lozinku</guimenuitem> da bi postavili "
"lozinku."

#. Tag: para
#: thumbnail-view.docbook:157
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Don't get fooled to believe that this will help you hide away images for "
"good. First the images are still on the disk, second, anyone with access to "
"the <filename>index.xml</filename> file that &kphotoalbum; uses can read the "
"password in clear text and optionally delete it. This feature is only meant "
"as a protection against someone sitting with &kphotoalbum; unintentionally "
"getting to your private images."
msgstr ""
"Nemojte se prevariti da povjerujute da će ovo pomoći da sakrjete slike za "
"stalno. Prvo slike su još uvijek na disku, drugo, neko sa pristupom na "
"<filename>index.xml</filename> datoteke čija &kphotoalbum; upotreba može "
"čitati lozinku sa jasnim tekstom i opcionalno je izbrisati. Ova osobina je "
"imala ulogu zaštite od nekoga koji dođe &kphotoalbum; i slučajno vidi vaše  "
"privatne slike."
